list.abstract: Plenty穿梭古今，美国品牌Tracy Reese的副线Plenty，设计以特色图案及鲜艳色彩为主，设计师Tracy Reese推出的主线系列，以其名字命名，服装以“Feminine Chin”民族服为主，设计成熟而女性化，以那些重视“可爱”形象的敏感细腻的女性为对象。趣怪的副线Plenty则色彩鲜明，设计异想天开，手工方面亦见细密，当中最巧妙是以现代工艺展现古典味，极具复古情调。

yingyinNormal.en: I make plenty of money! You make peanuts!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我挣了很多钱，你赚得塞牙缝都不够。

yingyinNormal.en: Yet Hong Kong offers plenty of green spaces too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但同时香港亦有很多绿化地点。

yingyinNormal.en: Hoho, we've plenty of time. It's only eleven o'clock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔喔，我们还有很多时间。现在才11点。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, you're here. We have plenty of room. No, we don't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看，你都来了，我们有很多房间的。不，我们没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Nice shovel shirt. They got plenty left. I don't see how.
yingyinNormal.zh: 铲子T恤衫真不错。他们店里还有很多呢。我真不明白怎么会卖不掉。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm so glad you could come Chandler, we've got plenty of food so I hope you're hungry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欢迎你来，有很多吃的，希望你饿了。

yingyinNormal.en: Skipping one day of school isn't gonna do any harm. I ditched plenty, and look at me today. I am fielding multiple job offers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 逃一天课不会怎么样的。我就逃了很多课，看看我现在，我得到了很多工作机会。

yingyinNormal.en: What can we do? There's plenty of petrol at my garage. I'II tow you there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们该怎么办？的修车厂就有很多汽油。我来拉你们过去。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Grandpa. We're already got plenty of potatoes. You can never have too many potatoes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，爷爷。我们已经挖了很多土豆了。土豆永远不嫌多。

yingyinNormal.en: And what are you doing working in that place? There're plenty of places besides that to work in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你究竟在那儿做什么呢？除了那儿还有很多地方可以去啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I got research. Plenty of people have been caught with unregistered guns and haven't gone to jail for it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我查过了，有很多因未注册枪支被抓的人都不用去坐牢。

yingyinNormal.en: I know plenty of relatives of English earls who belong in jail! I suppose we've made the decision.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道很多英国伯爵的亲戚都该去蹲监狱，看样子是已经决定了。

yingyinNormal.en: Our world is still plenty harsh and hostile, but now we know the Croods will make it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的世界仍然很艰苦，有很多敌人，但现在我们知道，咕噜一家能够解决这一切。

yingyinNormal.en: I happen to know a place where there are plenty of eligible women and Leonard could have his pick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我碰巧知道个好地方，有很多符合条件的女士，莱纳德可以任意选。

yingyinNormal.en: Why not? It's a great house, plenty of room, and if we have kids, Mom's there to help.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为何不住一起呢？那是个好房子， 很多屋子，如果我们有了孩子，我妈妈还能帮忙。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm trying to be a friend, Mrs. Florrick. I know. I have plenty of friends. I don't need any more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想和你做朋友，福瑞克夫人。我知道，我有很多朋友，不需要更多了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sure there'll be plenty of volunteers to keep up standards. Yeah? For how long? And what about the cricket?
yingyinNormal.zh: 相信会有很多人愿意出力，保证工程。是吗？要做多久？再说板球赛怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: So you're not going to Comic-Con? I've been plenty of times. If I miss one, it's fine. I'm a big boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你不去参加漫展了吗？反正我去过很多次了，小去一次也没关系，我是个成年人了。

yingyinNormal.en: Crisps are not on the list. We have plenty of crisps at home, Peppa. Have another guess. Hm. I just can't remember.
yingyinNormal.zh: 清单上没有薯片！家里有很多薯片，佩佩。再猜猜。嗯。 我想不起来了。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, she's great and it's not like we haven't done anything. I mean, we do plenty of other stuff, lot's of other stuff, like...
yingyinNormal.zh: 不！她很好，我们又不是什么都没做，我们做了很多事情，像是…

word_usage.usage:
用法plenty常与of连用，前不用a, plenty of可修饰可数或不可数名词。plenty of常用于肯定句，在否定句中表达此意常用enough，问句中可用enough或many或much：
There's plenty of rain this autumn.
今秋雨水充足。

word_usage.usage:
plenty of既可以修饰可数名词复数，也可以修饰不可数名词。
如：I have plenty of things to do.
我有很多事要做。
No need to hurry—you’ve got plenty of time.
没必要这么匆忙——你还有许多时间呢。
